The problem is that `total` variable is getting overwritten in each iterati
iteration of the loop instead of being incremented by the value of `item.co
`item.cost`. Therefore, to fix this, you need to add up the cost for each i
item and then print it out at the end. Here is the corrected version:

```tundra
val items = [
  { name: "a", cost: 2 },
  { name: "b", cost: 3 },
  { name: "c", cost: 4 }
];

var total = 0;
for(item in items) {
  total += item.cost;
}

print(total);
```
